Package: LDATree
Title: Classification Trees with Linear Discriminant Analysis Terminal
    Nodes
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Siyu", "Wang", , "swang739@wisc.edu", role = c("cre", "aut"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0009-0005-2098-7089"))
Description: A classification tree method that uses LDA (Linear
    Discriminant Analysis) for choosing variables, finding splits, and
    fitting models in terminal nodes.  Missing values are taken care of,
    and tools for visualization are provided.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/Moran79/LDATree, http://iamwangsiyu.com/LDATree/
